  "description": "swarmEnvAttack=2.5 seconds. At note-on, the boid forces are near zero — 128 particles scatter without collective intelligence, raw and disorganized. Over 2.5 seconds, the school learns its rules. Cohesion grows. Alignment grows. The scattered particles find each other and cohere into a tone. The note wakes up. Play slow, deliberate notes and wait. The instrument reveals itself on its own schedule.",
